Package otp.group6.audioeditor

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AudioCloudDAO
    AudioCloudDAO is a class that handles the database connection, user object and mixer settings object.
    AudioCloudDAO.MixerSetting
    MixerSettings class is used as an object to access the database mixer settings data in the main application.
    AudioCloudDAO.User
    Class Users is used as a object for the user while logged in.
    AudioCloudDAOTest
    Test class for AudioCloudDAO to check for different methods functionality with the database
    AudioFileHandler
    Class for handling audio files and audio input streams
    AudioManipulator
    AudioManipulator is a class that is used to create and operate the mixer.
    AudioManipulatorTest
    This test class is for testing the AudioManipulator.
    AudioOutput
    This class is used to play pack audio files
    AudioRecorder
    Provides tools for basic audio recording and playback of that recorded file
    AudioRecorderTest
    This test class is for AudioRecorder.
    PasswordUtils
    This class encrypts passwrods in Byte64.
    PasswordUtilsTest
    Test class for passwordUtils to check the functionality of the class
    Soundboard
    Soundboard class for storing and playing sampled audio
    SoundboardPlayer
    Audio player class for soundboard
    SoundboardTest
    Test class for soundboard
    SoundboardViewTest
    Test class for soundboard view
